{{Top}}
A '''napkin''' was a cloth used to clean an [[Species|individual's]] face. During the [[Amaxine warrior crisis]], a napkin was used to hide a piece of [[paper]] that bore the word "RUN." This outlaid plans to destroy the [[New Republic Senate conference building|senatorial conference building]] of the [[New Republic]] [[New Republic Senate|Senate]] on [[Hosnian Prime]] during the so-called "[[Napkin Bombing]]."<ref name="Bloodline">[[Bloodline (novel)|''Bloodline'']]</ref>

